\\[Subset] {1, 2, ..., n} for the fermionic Gaussian state characterized by \
n*n matrices G and F of the normal and anomalous Green's functions for n \
fermion modes. BravyiTimeReversalMoment[\\[Alpha], G n*n, {k1, k2, ...}] is \
equivalent to BravyiTimeReversalMoment[\\[Alpha], {G n*n, 0 n*n}, {k1, k2, \
